Package: collectr
Title: Quick Tool for Saving Visuals in a Unified Manner
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Vladimir", "Pyrlik", , "vpyrlik.gh@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: colelctr simplifies the process of gathering and organizing visual outputs in R projects. It aims to be an easy-to-use tool that allows you to collect visuals with consistent, predefined properties and later save them into a designated destination. 
